    <item>
      <title>石油市场疲软；沙特阿拉伯下调亚洲价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-06/oil-market-softens-saudi-arabia-cuts-asia-prices-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油价格连续第五天走低。主要市场指标表明供应超过需求，沙特阿拉伯将其对亚洲的官方原油售价下调至 2 月份以来的最高水平。苏基南在彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-06/oil-market-softens-saudi-arabia-cuts-asia-prices-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
