      <title>亚洲股市上涨，国债因美国就业机会上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场进一步放缓，加剧了美联储明年将降息以防止经济衰退的猜测，亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在向阿达尼提供贷款之前审查了兴登堡的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/us-examined-hindenburg-allegations-before-giving-loan-to-adani</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级官员表示，美国政府得出结论，卖空者兴登堡研究公司对印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的公司欺诈指控不适用于该集团的港口子公司，然后将该公司扩大到斯里兰卡一个集装箱码头，投资金额高达 5.53 亿美元。 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/us-examined-hindenburg-allegations-before-giving-loan-to-adani</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 03:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
